<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>404 — Page Not Found | PPCSet</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/logo.png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css?v=1.4" />
  <style>
    body { background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; margin: 0; }
    .error-container { text-align: center; }
    .error-title { font-size: 72px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .error-desc { font-size: 22px; color: #a0a0a0; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .error-btn { font-size: 18px; padding: 14px 36px; border-radius: 32px; background: #fff; color: #23272f; font-weight: 700; border: none; transition: background 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s; box-shadow: 0 2px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.10); cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .error-btn:hover { background: #ededed; transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.03); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.18); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="error-container">
    <div class="error-title">404</div>
    <div class="error-desc">Sorry, the page you are looking for does not exist.<br>Сторінка не знайдена або була видалена.</div>
    <a href="/" class="error-btn">Go to Home</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 